    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，branch2是从第一个commit a之后切出来的对吧？然后branch1上的commit b是在branch2已经走了f、g两步之后才提交的？",
      "elements_involved": [
