    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个顺序。还有，branch2的显示顺序我希望排在branch1右边，视觉上更清楚。另外commit标签要显示出来，方便演示的时候指认。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch2 order",
        "showCommitLabel",
        "showBranches"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先初始化配置，把日志级别设成debug方便排查，主题用base，然后开启分支显示和commit标签。branch1作为主分支，branch2的order设为1排在右侧。",
      "elements_involved": [
