      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，commit b之后checkout branch2那一步其实可以省略，因为merge branch1本身就会切过去。不过你画出来也行，更明确。但commit id我确认一下：a、f、g、b这四个字母对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
